<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/798945-i-haven-t-read-fall-of-the-giants-but-i">I haven&#39;t read Fall of the Giants, but I do have a copy of Winter of the World which I&#39;d love to start right away. How connected are the two books, and would I be okay if I start with Winter, see how I flow with it, and then come back to Fall?

Thanks in advance for the help.</a>
</div>
